Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮帮忙\N{\fs12}helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为来这里的都是  呃\N{\fs12}Uh, l thought this was just for, uh--
