Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,罗兹  这是伯顿·法林  由他来处理特伦斯的收养案子\N{\fs12}Roz, this is Burton Fallin. He's handling Terence's adoption.
