Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,特伦斯的出生是个意外\N{\fs12}And Terence here was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我要做这个的原因\N{\fs12}That's why l'm doing this.
