Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs12}There ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好激动  这些孩子明天就会\N{\fs12}Well, it's gonna be exciting all these kids being--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在一天之内都会被收养\N{\fs12}having their adoptions finalized on one day.
