Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在已经跟新的家庭生活在一起了\N{\fs12}And they're already living with their families,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是还需要法官来宣布它的合法性  所以\N{\fs12}but it takes a judge to make it legal so...
