Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莎迪赛德  - 莎迪赛德\N{\fs12}- Shadyside. - Shadyside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来自莎迪赛德的打工的可不多\N{\fs12}Not a lot of laborers from Shadyside.
