Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,独自学习的人  莎迪赛德\N{\fs12}The doer alone learneth, Shadyside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs12}What's that?
