Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,加快速度  法林  我们不能光刷漆就刷一个月\N{\fs12}Get your back into it, Franklin. We can't spend a month out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,查克上个月监督我高速公路清理的工作\N{\fs12}Chuck supervised me last month-- highway clean-up.
