Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs12}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的钱包\N{\fs12}My wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  当你帮我打官司的时候  我真的很尊敬你\N{\fs12}You know, when you represented me l really looked up to you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,帮了我之后  我以为你所做的\N{\fs12}After you helped me out, l thought what you did--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你人真很好\N{\fs12}thought you were, like, the greatest guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就偷走了我的钱包吗\N{\fs12}So you did steal my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是不明白\N{\fs12}You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你一但成年了\N{\fs12}Uh, once you're eighteen--
