Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天  很多人帮助我\N{\fs12}l mean, one day l had all this help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,社会劳动者表现得有多在乎我一样\N{\fs12}Social workers acting like that you gave a crap about me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,接着第二天\N{\fs12}and then the next day--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我就得自己靠自己了\N{\fs12}Well, the next day, l was on my own, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时非常迷茫\N{\fs12}Yeah, l was totally lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这时我遇到一个人  他说如果我把我的助学贷款给他投资\N{\fs12}So then this guy, you see, he tells me if l invest my school loan money with him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以在一周或者一个月之内双倍给我\N{\fs12}he can, like, double it in a week or a month or something, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就把钱给他了\N{\fs12}So l give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真聪明  - 这个人跟我说\N{\fs12}- That was smart. - This guy, he said
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他把钱都输在了生物技术的股票上了  但是\N{\fs12}he, uh-- he said he lost it all on some biotech stock, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就给你打电话  但是你从没给我回过电话\N{\fs12}So then l called you to see if you might help and you never called me back.
