Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而且大学  他们没有收到我的学费\N{\fs12}And the college, right? See, they're weren't paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也拿不出钱去缴学费  对吧\N{\fs12}And l can't come up with the money, right?
