Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,需要做很多次手术  而且康复期很长\N{\fs12}lt's gonna take several surgeries and a long rehabilitation period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
