Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最少\N{\fs12}Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,罗恩  你已经研究这个案子一整天了\N{\fs12}Ron, you've been working on this case one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  这次会议我可以给你20000美元\N{\fs12}l mean, you're walking away with $20,000 for one meeting.
