Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以想象下  最好的高中  最好的大学\N{\fs12}Well, you can imagine, you know, the best high schools, college,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,研究生学位和一份稳定的工作\N{\fs12}and graduate degree. A solid job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在说  我给不了这些\N{\fs12}And you're saying l can't provide those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你给不了  罗伊\N{\fs12}l'm not so sure you can, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  香农可以成为任何她\N{\fs12}See Shannon could be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,想成为的人\N{\fs12}whatever she wants to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有着你和我那个年代没有的\N{\fs12}Have the opportunities to make choices that, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,选择的机会\N{\fs12}well, you and l never had when we were growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我想说的\N{\fs12}That's what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给香农更多的选择\N{\fs12}Having options for Shannon, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以之前有个律师小姐给我打电话\N{\fs12}So that lawyer lady that called
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说了一些关于要不要选择\N{\fs12}said something about, should l choose to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃香农的抚养权的事\N{\fs12}that l'd be terminating my parental responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你会的\N{\fs12}You would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能不能考虑一下  -当然\N{\fs12}- l have time to think about it? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你签字了\N{\fs12}Oh, and if you do sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有四十天的反悔时间\N{\fs12}there will be a forty day revocation period, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吗  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Okay? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  我回来了\N{\fs12}Burton, l'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Hey, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  罗伊\N{\fs12}Hey, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Hey, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,给你买的\N{\fs12}This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我给社区大学财务室的\N{\fs12}So l called that guy at the community college,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人打电话了  他愿意给我重新制定一个还款计划\N{\fs12}bursar's office, and he's willing to set up a payment schedule with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我付了前三期的款  他们会重新给我发放他们的贷款\N{\fs12}And, if l keep up my first three payments, they'll re-issue my loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不错啊  - 是的\N{\fs12}- There ya go. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是  我现在没有工作\N{\fs12}See the thing is, though l don't have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  谢谢你\N{\fs12}l mean, thanks and that, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我现在没有办法偿还任何钱\N{\fs12}l can't really amord to pay anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我找一份工作吗\N{\fs12}Uh, can you help me get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}Well, l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄  你们律师所里肯定有人可以帮我找到一份工作吧\N{\fs12}Oh, come on. You must know somebody at the clinic who can help me get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.87,0:24:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,富兰克林  我希望你给每个人\N{\fs12}Franklin, l hope you brought
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都买了一杯咖啡\N{\fs12}enough coffee for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以问你个问题吗\N{\fs12}Ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你说\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.97,0:24:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我交了个女朋友  她叫辛迪\N{\fs12}l got this girlfriend. Her name's Cindy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.79,0:24:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她来自福克斯教堂\N{\fs12}She's from Fox Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.20,0:24:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她在卡耐基·梅隆大学学戏剧专业\N{\fs12}She's a-- she's a drama major at Carnegie Mellon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她想成为一名电影明星\N{\fs12}She wants to be a movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.23,0:24:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也跟她说了我也在卡耐基·梅隆大学念书\N{\fs12}So l've been telling Cindy that, you know, that l go to CMU.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我学的是计算机\N{\fs12}That l'm working with computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉她我是个孤儿\N{\fs12}You know, if l told her l was an orphan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.86,0:24:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,或者告诉她我甚至没有上过社区大学\N{\fs12}or who doesn't even go to community college--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我还因为偷盗信用卡被处缓刑\N{\fs12}You know, who's on probation for stealing credit cards, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,女生肯定都不想听到这些\N{\fs12}That's not exactly what a girl like that wants to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.54,0:24:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 肯定不想  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- No. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许  如果你帮我找到了一份工作\N{\fs12}So maybe, like, if you can help me get a job
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.81,0:24:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我能重新去学校念书  也许她就会觉得和我在一起以后会有希望\N{\fs12}and that and l re-enroll in school then she'll think l'm a guy with a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.26,0:24:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是  也许她会\N{\fs12}Yeah, she might.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.56,0:25:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs12}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.61,0:25:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我\N{\fs12}Thanks for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.34,0:25:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,罗兹  你怎么样了\N{\fs12}How are you, Roz?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.34,0:25:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很疼\N{\fs12}l'm-- It hurts a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.04,0:25:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}l'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.97,0:25:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我\N{\fs12}Listen, l--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.43,0:25:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想\N{\fs12}l just--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.02,0:25:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把特伦斯要回来\N{\fs12}l want Terence back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.12,0:25:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.72,0:25:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要她的唯一的原因就是我养不起她\N{\fs12}The only reason l gave him up was because l couldn't amord another kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.13,0:25:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我们能不能就当这些都没有发生过\N{\fs12}So if we could just tear everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你都签了字了\N{\fs12}But, you signed the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.48,0:25:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,文件上写着我可以改变主意\N{\fs12}The form said l could change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当初给你时间考虑了\N{\fs12}But, you had a time period
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.46,0:25:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,时间已经过了  对不对  法林先生\N{\fs12}that's run out. Right, Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这不在我的专业范围内\N{\fs12}Well, this is not my area of expertise
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.09,0:25:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是确实  你的撤销的时间已经过去了  但是\N{\fs12}but, yeah, your revocation period has come and gone, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.29,0:25:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是收养的程序还没有通过\N{\fs12}But the adoption hasn't gone through yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.66,0:26:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不行  他是我们的了\N{\fs12}No. This is-- No. He's ours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.37,0:26:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经走完程序了\N{\fs12}We've been through the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.86,0:26:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明天只是走个流程而已\N{\fs12}Tomorrow is just supposed to be a formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.78,0:26:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你  把特伦斯还给我\N{\fs12}Please, give Terence back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.40,0:26:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我\N{\fs12}Give him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.05,0:26:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.55,0:26:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  我的当事人要求每周有两个小时的探望时间\N{\fs12}Your Honor, my client requests two hours of supervised visitation per week
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.10,0:26:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每个月可以有一个星期天可以去看孩子\N{\fs12}as well as one Sunday a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.45,0:26:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果劳拉想要探望孩子  在安排探望之前\N{\fs12}lf any visitations are scheduled my clients would like them
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.52,0:26:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的当事人必须知道劳拉的\N{\fs12}to be contingent upon Laura's successful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.31,0:26:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,戒毒康复情况是成功的\N{\fs12}completion of a drug rehabilitation program.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.61,0:26:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的法官大人  劳拉·唐纳龙原因\N{\fs12}Well, Your Honor, Laura Donnellon is willing to enter
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.01,0:26:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,进入戒毒所接受治疗\N{\fs12}a drug treatment program,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她要求立刻有接触孩子的权利\N{\fs12}but she would like immediate access to her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.41,0:26:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,重申  我方当事人只有在劳拉康复之前\N{\fs12}Again, my clients are only willing to take
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.00,0:26:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不允许接触孩子\N{\fs12}the child if their daughter is not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.95,0:26:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,才能答应会收留孩子\N{\fs12}access until after her rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.39,0:26:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,否则  尽管他们会很难过\N{\fs12}OtheM/ise, as much as this pains them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们也不会收留孩子\N{\fs12}they will not take the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.96,0:26:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  我能说话吗\N{\fs12}Your Honor, may l speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.99,0:26:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请说\N{\fs12}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.21,0:27:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尼采说  家庭的爱\N{\fs12}Um, Nietzsche wrote that family love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.73,0:27:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是令人苦恼及不断重复的混乱模式\N{\fs12}is messy of an annoying and repetitive pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.05,0:27:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是坏掉地墙纸\N{\fs12}Like bad wallpaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.75,0:27:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉  对我父母来说\N{\fs12}And l've been kinda like that to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.15,0:27:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不断重复这些  非常让人讨厌\N{\fs12}l mean, repetitive in my actions and probably more than annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.97,0:27:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\N{\fs12}What l mean to say is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.29,0:27:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想回家\N{\fs12}that l would like to go home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.26,0:27:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果\N{\fs12}lf, um--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.50,0:27:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我现在说还来得及的话\N{\fs12}if this is an appropriate time to say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.89,0:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这里是讨论收留你的女儿的问题的\N{\fs12}We are here only to discuss the placement of your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.13,0:27:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对  抱歉\N{\fs12}Right. l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.87,0:27:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果劳拉·唐纳龙想要去探望佛吉尼亚的话\N{\fs12}lf Laura Donnellon wishes to visit Virginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.40,0:27:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她必须提前一天通知\N{\fs12}she must give twenty-four hours' notice
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.41,0:27:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她是清醒的\N{\fs12}and she must be sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.32,0:28:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的当事人接受\N{\fs12}My clients accept the terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.55,0:28:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是板上钉钉的事情  对不对\N{\fs12}This is a done deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.67,0:28:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  他们不能把特伦斯带走\N{\fs12}l mean, they can't make us give Terence back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.10,0:28:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定  但是\N{\fs12}l'm not sure, but, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.13,0:28:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经不要特伦斯了\N{\fs12}She already walked away from Terence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也签了那些文件\N{\fs12}She signed the forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.66,0:28:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可撤销期也已经过了\N{\fs12}She waited through the revocation period.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.54,0:28:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,事情已经结束了\N{\fs12}lt's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.14,0:28:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  那我们继续弄收养的程序把\N{\fs12}Fine, let's just move on with the adoption proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.06,0:28:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你说得对\N{\fs12}l think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.40,0:28:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,罗兹确实说过因为她养不起这个孩子她才放弃她得\N{\fs12}Roz did say that she only gave up the baby because she couldn't amord him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.63,0:28:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.51,0:28:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在有照顾特伦斯的钱了\N{\fs12}And now she has the money to take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.46,0:28:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果她不想给我们的话  我不知道\N{\fs12}So l don't know if l can take this baby from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.76,0:28:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我能不能从她身边抢走这个孩子\N{\fs12}if she doesn't want to give him to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.74,0:28:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,利雅\N{\fs12}Ria.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.99,0:29:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fs12}l can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.13,0:29:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能要这个孩子\N{\fs12}l can't take this baby
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.55,0:29:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她不想给我们的话\N{\fs12}if she doesn't want to give him to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.76,0:29:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们做决定之前\N{\fs12}Look, let's just meet with the judge
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先去法庭听听法官怎么说  好吗\N{\fs12}first before you decide anything. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.88,0:29:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我太蠢了  我看起来就像个傻逼一样\N{\fs12}l was so stupid. l made a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.73,0:29:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  你没有  你刚才很棒\N{\fs12}No, you didn't. You were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.39,0:29:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你的父母谈过了\N{\fs12}l, uh-- l talked to your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.31,0:29:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们安排了明天早上开个会\N{\fs12}We scheduled a meeting tomorrow morning.
