Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.48,0:36:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  一次又一次\N{\fs12}Yeah... in one iteration. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.79,0:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一次又一次\N{\fs12}ln one iteration?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.59,0:37:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你父亲的问题  你还不能放手吗\N{\fs12}These problems with your dad, are they worth dying over?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.79,0:37:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这太伤人了\N{\fs12}That's melodramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这种人活不久的\N{\fs12}People like you don't survive very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.26,0:37:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 像我  - 对  像你这种人\N{\fs12}- Like me? - Yeah, like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.90,0:37:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的选择\N{\fs12}This is my choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.15,0:37:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么以开始还是回到了匹兹堡呢\N{\fs12}Why did you come back to Pittsburgh in the first place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.07,0:37:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你这么恨你父母  你为什么还要回来呢\N{\fs12}lf you hate your parents so much, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.99,0:37:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想让他们帮我照顾我的孩子们\N{\fs12}l just want them to take care of my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.17,0:37:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了  啊\N{\fs12}What happened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.49,0:37:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前还说你想跟你父母一起住的\N{\fs12}You said you wanted to live with your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.22,0:37:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  那是你说的\N{\fs12}No, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.12,0:37:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  帮我告诉他们好吗\N{\fs12}So you... Just tell them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.48,0:37:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们  谢谢他们\N{\fs12}Tell them thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.23,0:38:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我们抓到一个\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, we detained a young man
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.79,0:38:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想要从你的支票账户提取5000美元的男子\N{\fs12}who attempted to withdraw five thousand dollars from your checking account.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.09,0:38:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他掌握了你的所有信息\N{\fs12}He had all of your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.86,0:38:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本来要报警了\N{\fs12}Now, we were going to call the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.36,0:38:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他说你认识他  而且他这么做是经过你允许的\N{\fs12}but he insisted that you knew he was here and had given your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.56,0:38:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要不要报警\N{\fs12}Would you like us to call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.03,0:38:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿  你知道我以后肯定会还你钱的\N{\fs12}Hey. Hey, you know l would... l would've paid you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.68,0:38:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想给辛迪买那个戒指\N{\fs12}l... l just... l wanted to get that ring for Cindy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.10,0:38:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我很感激你没有报警\N{\fs12}l really appreciate you not taking this badly, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.85,0:38:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常感谢你\N{\fs12}l mean, uh... l really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.20,0:38:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗  如果领养一旦生效\N{\fs12}Do you understand that if this adoption decree is granted,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.53,0:39:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利就像所有的亲生婴儿一样\N{\fs12}Henry will be the same as a natural child?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.64,0:39:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.80,0:39:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你将有义务去教育  帮助\N{\fs12}That you will have the duty to educate, support,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.13,0:39:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,教导和培养他\N{\fs12}and provide moral guidance and upbringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.53,0:39:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.43,0:39:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你将有责任去关怀爱护他\N{\fs12}That you have a duty of love and affection to show to this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.86,0:39:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.11,0:39:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以继承你的财产  你也可以接受他的财产\N{\fs12}That he may inherit from you and you from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.44,0:39:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.39,0:39:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在他和未来你可能拥有的\N{\fs12}That there can be no discrimination between this child
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.47,0:39:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子之间不会有歧视\N{\fs12}and any natural or adopted child you may have now or in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.83,0:39:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.43,0:39:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在明白了上述责任之后  你们希望收养亨利吗\N{\fs12}Understanding these responsibilities, do you wish to adopt Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.36,0:39:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.23,0:39:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  我同意此收养令生效\N{\fs12}Your Honor, l move the adoption degree be... be entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.16,0:39:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定了\N{\fs12}So ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.40,0:39:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fs12}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.78,0:39:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  法林先生\N{\fs12}Thank you, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.73,0:40:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚给辛迪打电话了\N{\fs12}So l tried to call Cindy last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.14,0:40:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是不想跟我讲话\N{\fs12}She still won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.51,0:40:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我要忘记她了\N{\fs12}Yeah, so... l'm over her, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你说得对  你猜怎么着\N{\fs12}Hey, and you're right. You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.48,0:40:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,社区大学里会有很多靓妞的\N{\fs12}There are lots of hot girls at community college.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.98,0:40:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不会那么自大\N{\fs12}Not so, uh, stuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.83,0:40:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不错  对吧\N{\fs12}That looks good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.01,0:40:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,富兰克林  有个地方漏刷了\N{\fs12}Franklin, you missed a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.40,0:41:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  我朋友叫尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Hey, my friend's name is Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.22,0:41:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不叫富兰克林  是法林\N{\fs12}Not Franklin. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.27,0:41:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  但是还是漏了一块\N{\fs12}Well, he missed a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.95,0:41:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  你没有漏刷\N{\fs12}You know... you didn't miss a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.74,0:41:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  对不对\N{\fs12}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.37,0:41:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  莎迪赛德人\N{\fs12}Hey, Shadyside.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.19,0:41:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.11,0:41:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,天气变冷了\N{\fs12}lt's getting cold.
